"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:7.4.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">7.4.2</span> 標題：鈸、鐃鈸（cymbals）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מְצִלְתַּיִם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mtsiltayim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr13:8\">1CH 13:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:16\">1CH 15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:19\">1CH 15:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:28\">1CH 15:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:5\">1CH 16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:42\">1CH 16:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr25:1\">1CH 25:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr25:6\">1CH 25:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:12\">2CH 5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:13\">2CH 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:25\">2CH 29:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:10\">EZR 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:27\">NEH 12:27</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： צֶלְצְלִים</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： tseltselim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:5\">2SA 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:5\">PSA 150:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:5\">PSA 150:5</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： κύμβαλον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： kumbalon)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:1\">1CO 13:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt16:1\">JDT 16:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc4:54\">1MA 4:54</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc13:51\">1MA 13:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd5:57\">1ES 5:57</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0514_cymbals.jpg\" alt=\"鈸\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">鈸 (© Finoskov, CC BY-SA 4.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>鈸是一種打擊樂器，由兩塊金屬圓盤組成，圓盤互相撞擊，發出尖銳、刺耳的聲音。鈸有兩種類型：（1）兩個扁平金屬薄片互相撞擊；（2）兩個圓錐形金屬片，將其中一片的敞開側從上往下碰擊另一片的敞開側。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在許多語言中，「鈸」的對等譯法是「響亮的金屬」之類短語。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:5\">PSA 150:5</a> 提到了兩種鈸，字面意思分別是「聽鈸」和「喊鈸」。這可能是指「小鈸……大鈸」，也可能是比較詩意的表達方式，實際意思為「響鈸……撞鈸」。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:1\">1CO 13:1</a> 中，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 把希臘文<em>kumbalon</em> 譯為「鐘」（“bell”）而不是「鈸」，因為鐘更為人所熟知。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
